Principles for minimalist design in mobile apps:
- Use only essential elements on screen.
- Apply a neutral color palette with one accent color.
- Simple and consistent typography, without excess.
- Clear and direct navigation.
- Generous spacing to improve readability.
- Simple icons without unnecessary decorations.
- Smooth and subtle animations, if any.
- Prioritize functionality over ornamentation.
